𝗗𝗮𝘆 𝟴: 𝗔𝗴𝗶𝗹𝗶𝘁𝘆 𝗠𝗲𝗮𝗻𝘀 𝗙𝗹𝗲𝘅𝗶𝗯𝗶𝗹𝗶𝘁𝘆!
🚀 "Agility is about adapting fast—be the first to flex!"  
👉 𝗧𝗶𝗽: Encourage your team to embrace change rather than resist it. Flexibility is key to thriving in uncertainty.

💡 𝗗𝗮𝗶𝗹𝘆 𝘁𝗶𝗽𝘀 for Scrum Teams and especially Scrum Masters! Get practical advice, best practices, & strategies to boost collaboration and sprint success.
